{"capsule_id": "claude_code_2025_07_14_11053d41d7154dc6", "type": "reasoning_trace", "content": "Claude Code interaction: how do i implement authentication in my flask app?...", "input_data": "how do i implement authentication in my flask app?", "output": "Here's how to implement authentication in Flask:\n\n```python\nfrom flask import Flask, request, jsonify\nfrom functools import wraps\nimport jwt\n\ndef token_required(f):\n    @wraps(f)\n    def decorated(*args, **kwargs):\n        token = request.headers.get('Authorization')\n        if not token:\n            return jsonify({'error': 'Token missing'}), 401\n        try:\n            data = jwt.decode(token, app.config['SECRET_KEY'])\n        except:\n            return jsonify({'error': 'Token invalid'}), 401\n        return f(*args, **kwargs)\n    return decorated\n```\n\nThis decorator will protect your routes...", "reasoning": "[{\"step_type\": \"significance_detection\", \"content\": \"Code generation detected\", \"weight\": 0.1, \"timestamp\": \"2025-07-14T22:40:52.453161\"}, {\"step_type\": \"significance_detection\", \"content\": \"Learning/explanation content\", \"weight\": 0.15000000000000002, \"timestamp\": \"2025-07-14T22:40:52.453164\"}, {\"step_type\": \"significance_detection\", \"content\": \"Technical depth in response\", \"weight\": 0.2, \"timestamp\": \"2025-07-14T22:40:52.453166\"}]", "model_version": "claude-sonnet-4-conversation-monitor", "timestamp": "2025-07-14T22:40:52.453073Z", "agent_id": "claude-code-auto-capsule-system", "status": "SEALED", "metadata": {"interaction_type": "claude_code_conversation", "session_id": "c44069d2", "turn_id": "turn_002", "significance_score": 0.7, "decision_factors": ["Code generation detected", "Learning/explanation content", "Technical depth in response"], "confidence": 0.8, "auto_selected": true, "user_id": "kay", "conversation_length": 654, "reasoning_quality": "automated_significance_analysis"}}
