{"capsule_id": "windsurf_2025_07_15_834edfe9f51b418b", "type": "reasoning_trace", "content": "Windsurf IDE interaction: What's the best way to optimize this API call?...", "input_data": "What's the best way to optimize this API call?", "output": "Here are several optimization strategies for your API call:\n\n1. **Caching**: Implement response caching\n2. **Debouncing**: Prevent excessive calls\n3. **Pagination**: Load data in chunks\n4. **Compression**: Use gzip compression\n5. **Connection pooling**: Reuse connections\n\nExample with caching:\n```javascript\nconst cache = new Map();\n\nasync function optimizedApiCall(url) {\n  if (cache.has(url)) {\n    return cache.get(url);\n  }\n  \n  const response = await fetch(url);\n  const data = await response.json();\n  cache.set(url, data);\n  return data;\n}\n```", "reasoning": "[{\"step_type\": \"windsurf_significance_detection\", \"content\": \"Code generation detected\", \"weight\": 0.1, \"timestamp\": \"2025-07-15T10:33:40.961073\"}, {\"step_type\": \"windsurf_significance_detection\", \"content\": \"Learning/explanation content\", \"weight\": 0.15000000000000002, \"timestamp\": \"2025-07-15T10:33:40.961080\"}, {\"step_type\": \"windsurf_significance_detection\", \"content\": \"Problem-solving discussion\", \"weight\": 0.2, \"timestamp\": \"2025-07-15T10:33:40.961083\"}, {\"step_type\": \"windsurf_significance_detection\", \"content\": \"Technical depth in response\", \"weight\": 0.25, \"timestamp\": \"2025-07-15T10:33:40.961087\"}, {\"step_type\": \"windsurf_significance_detection\", \"content\": \"Workflow improvement discussion\", \"weight\": 0.30000000000000004, \"timestamp\": \"2025-07-15T10:33:40.961090\"}, {\"step_type\": \"windsurf_significance_detection\", \"content\": \"Performance optimization\", \"weight\": 0.35, \"timestamp\": \"2025-07-15T10:33:40.961093\"}]", "model_version": "windsurf-conversation-monitor", "timestamp": "2025-07-15T10:33:40.961147Z", "agent_id": "windsurf-auto-capsule-system", "statu